docs {
  ## Send Test Email Using Current Config
  ส่งเมลทดสอบด้วย report_email config ปัจจุบัน

  Sends a test email through the normal BU notification flow (load config → decrypt → send) so the result mirrors production behavior.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": { "sent": true },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Test email sent successfully",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | SMTP config not found or misconfigured for this business unit |
}
